@node BESCH "Description"

-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-
@{fg highlight} - Description -@{fg text}
-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-

  @{b}Mega/Space@{ub} watches the capacity of as many disks as you like and
  the amount of free memory and starts actions when the defined minimums are
  reached. If these actions don't lead to more disk space or free memory, the
  system can be completely stopped.

@endnode
@node VORR "Requirements"

-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-
@{fg highlight} - Requirements -@{fg text}
-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-/-=*=-

  @{b}Mega/Space@{ub} needs OS 2.04 and MUI 2.3.

@endnode
@node CDWARE "CD-Ware"

